# Keep the build context small. On the VPS the context is a fresh git checkout
# (no node_modules), but locally our cwd has them — exclude heavy/irrelevant paths.
# Do NOT ignore `.env` — the Dockerfile copies the context-root `.env` into the build.
**/node_modules
**/.svelte-kit
**/build
**/.vercel
site/.data
**/*.log
.git
.github
.issues
.knowledge
ids-import
python-scripts
scripts
archive
cf-worker
